\begin{lem}\label{lem:2.1} The code ${\mathcal GRS}_k({\bf a},{\bf v},\infty)$ defined in {\rm \eqref{eq:2.2}} is a $q$-ary $[n+1,k,n+2-k]$-MDS code.
